sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sys_transform_script"><sys_transform_script action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><active>true</active><map display_value="u_imp_saml_user_p5hm1sghog">670961acdba34740249c771ebf961942</map><order>100</order><script><![CDATA[ //Send data to usage analytics.
 //sso_source is 'sso:' followed by the idp sys id. Hence 'sso:' needs to be removed
if (action == 'insert')
    SNC.SecurityEventSender.sendEventData('SAML.User.AutoProvisioning.Create', 
'user_name=' + target.first_name, 'idp sysid=' + target.sso_source.substring(4));
else if (action == 'update' && target.changes())
    SNC.SecurityEventSender.sendEventData('SAML.User.AutoProvisioning.Update', 
'user_name=' + target.first_name, 'idp sysid=' + target.sso_source.substring(4));
]]></script><sys_class_name>sys_transform_script</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>anthony.dotson@five9.com</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2018-01-05 22:49:34</sys_created_on><sys_customer_update>true</sys_customer_update><sys_id>ef0961acdba34740249c771ebf961959</sys_id><sys_mod_count>0</sys_mod_count><sys_name>onAfter</sys_name><sys_package display_value="Five9 Plus Adapter" source="x_f9_five9_adapter">48cb0035db03f200249c771ebf961905</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_replace_on_upgrade>false</sys_replace_on_upgrade><sys_scope display_value="Five9 Plus Adapter">48cb0035db03f200249c771ebf961905</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_transform_script_ef0961acdba34740249c771ebf961959</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>anthony.dotson@five9.com</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2018-01-05 22:49:34</sys_updated_on><when>onAfter</when></sys_transform_script></record_update>

sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update sys_domain="global" table="sys_script"><sys_script action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><abort_action>false</abort_action><access>package_private</access><action_delete>true</action_delete><action_insert>true</action_insert><action_query>false</action_query><action_update>true</action_update><active>true</active><add_message>false</add_message><advanced>true</advanced><change_fields>false</change_fields><client_callable>false</client_callable><collection>x_f9_five9_adapter_five9_entity_configuration</collection><condition/><description/><execute_function>false</execute_function><filter_condition/><is_rest>false</is_rest><message/><name>Five9 Update OpenFrame For Entity</name><order>100</order><priority>100</priority><rest_method/><rest_method_text/><rest_service/><rest_service_text/><rest_variables/><role_conditions/><script><![CDATA[(function executeRule(current, previous /*null when async*/) {
        gs.info("executeRule: " + current);
	var mainRec = new GlideRecord('x_f9_five9_adapter_five9_openframe_configuration');
	var config = {};
	mainRec.query();   
	if (mainRec.next()) {   
		config.bringapptofront = mainRec.getValue("bringapptofront");
		config.preselected_campaignname = mainRec.getValue("preselected_campaignname");
		config.recordinglinkurl = mainRec.getValue("recordinglinkurl");
		config.scriptedapiurl = mainRec.getValue("scriptedapiurl");	
		config.bringapptofront = mainRec.getValue("bringapptofront");
		config.phone_log_table = mainRec.getValue("phone_log");
		config.preselected_campaignname = mainRec.getValue("preselected_campaignname");
		config.recordinglinkurl = mainRec.getValue("recordinglinkurl");
		config.scriptedapiurl = mainRec.getValue("scriptedapiurl");
		config.client_id = mainRec.getValue("client_id");
		config.instance_url = mainRec.getValue("instance_url");
	}
	var entity = new GlideRecord('x_f9_five9_adapter_five9_entity_configuration');
	var entities = [];
	entity.query(); 
	while (entity.next()) {   
		var rec = {};
		rec.entity = entity.getValue("entity");
		rec.close_results = entity.getValue("close_results");
		rec.label = entity.getValue("label");
		rec.value = entity.getValue("value");
		rec.query = entity.getValue("query");
		rec.save_notes = entity.getValue("save_notes");
		rec.staging = entity.getValue("staging");
		rec.add_new_record = entity.getValue("add_new_record");
		rec.new_record_parameters = entity.getValue("new_record_parameters");
                rec.phone_format = entity.getValue("phone_format");
		entities.push(rec);
		var json2 =  new global.JSON().encode(rec);
	}
					
	var json =  new global.JSON().encode(entities);
	//gs.addInfoMessage(json);
	
	config.entityFieldMap = entities;
	var configJson =  new global.JSON().encode(config);
	//gs.addInfoMessage(configJson);
	
	// Now update the openframe configuration
	var openFrame = new GlideRecord('sn_openframe_configuration');
	var ofconfig = {};
        openFrame.addQuery("name", "Five9AdapterConfiguration");
	openFrame.query();   
	if (openFrame.next()) {  
		openFrame.setValue("configuration", configJson);
		openFrame.update();
	}
})(current, previous);]]></script><sys_class_name>sys_script</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>anthony.dotson@five9.com</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2017-06-22 19:03:58</sys_created_on><sys_customer_update>true</sys_customer_update><sys_domain>global</sys_domain><sys_domain_path>/</sys_domain_path><sys_id>4878790ddb23fa00249c771ebf9619f0</sys_id><sys_mod_count>39</sys_mod_count><sys_name>Five9 Update OpenFrame For Entity</sys_name><sys_overrides/><sys_package display_value="Five9 Plus Adapter" source="x_f9_five9_adapter">48cb0035db03f200249c771ebf961905</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_replace_on_upgrade>false</sys_replace_on_upgrade><sys_scope display_value="Five9 Plus Adapter">48cb0035db03f200249c771ebf961905</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_script_4878790ddb23fa00249c771ebf9619f0</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>anthony.dotson@five9.com</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2017-11-14 15:59:05</sys_updated_on><template>staging=^EQ</template><when>after</when></sys_script><sys_translated_text action="delete_multiple" query="documentkey=4878790ddb23fa00249c771ebf9619f0"/></record_update>

<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sys_transform_map"><sys_transform_map action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><active>true</active><copy_empty_fields>false</copy_empty_fields><enforce_mandatory_fields>No</enforce_mandatory_fields><name>u_imp_saml_user_p5hm1sghog</name><order>100</order><run_business_rules>false</run_business_rules><run_script>true</run_script><script><![CDATA[//This is important for the first ever login, otherwise an empty user may be created
//until a Field Map is defined below - It's recommended to use the same field for coalescing
//as defined in SSO user_field or nameid attribute field
if(action == "insert") {
    //if no coalesce is set, then ignore insert
    if(!coalesceIsSet()) {
        ignore = true;
        gs.log("No coalesce is set, insert is ignored!");
    } 
}

//Returns true is coalesce field has been set for this
//transform map, false otherwise
function coalesceIsSet() {
    var fieldMap = new GlideRecord("sys_transform_entry");
    fieldMap.addQuery("map.name", "u_imp_saml_user_p5hm1sghog");
    fieldMap.addQuery("coalesce", true);
    fieldMap.query();
    return fieldMap.hasNext();
}
]]></script><source_table>u_imp_saml_user_p5hm1sghog</source_table><sys_class_name>sys_transform_map</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>anthony.dotson@five9.com</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2018-01-05 22:49:34</sys_created_on><sys_customer_update>true</sys_customer_update><sys_id>670961acdba34740249c771ebf961942</sys_id><sys_mod_count>0</sys_mod_count><sys_name>u_imp_saml_user_p5hm1sghog</sys_name><sys_package display_value="Five9 Plus Adapter" source="x_f9_five9_adapter">48cb0035db03f200249c771ebf961905</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_replace_on_upgrade>false</sys_replace_on_upgrade><sys_scope display_value="Five9 Plus Adapter">48cb0035db03f200249c771ebf961905</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_transform_map_670961acdba34740249c771ebf961942</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>anthony.dotson@five9.com</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2018-01-05 22:49:34</sys_updated_on><target_table>sys_user</target_table></sys_transform_map></record_update>

sys_update_xml.name: sys_transform_script_d7f65c49db724300249c771ebf9619ac
sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sys_transform_script"><sys_transform_script action="DELETE"><active>true</active><map display_value="">c3f65c49db724300249c771ebf9619a2</map><order>100</order><script><![CDATA[ //Send data to usage analytics.
 //sso_source is 'sso:' followed by the idp sys id. Hence 'sso:' needs to be removed
if (action == 'insert')
    SNC.SecurityEventSender.sendEventData('SAML.User.AutoProvisioning.Create', 
'user_name=' + target.first_name, 'idp sysid=' + target.sso_source.substring(4));
else if (action == 'update' && target.changes())
    SNC.SecurityEventSender.sendEventData('SAML.User.AutoProvisioning.Update', 
'user_name=' + target.first_name, 'idp sysid=' + target.sso_source.substring(4));
]]></script><sys_class_name>sys_transform_script</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>anthony.dotson@five9.com</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2017-11-30 23:20:52</sys_created_on><sys_customer_update>true</sys_customer_update><sys_id>d7f65c49db724300249c771ebf9619ac</sys_id><sys_mod_count>0</sys_mod_count><sys_name>onAfter</sys_name><sys_package display_value="Five9 Adapter for ServiceNow" source="x_f9_five9_adapter">48cb0035db03f200249c771ebf961905</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_replace_on_upgrade>false</sys_replace_on_upgrade><sys_scope display_value="Five9 Adapter for ServiceNow">48cb0035db03f200249c771ebf961905</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_transform_script_d7f65c49db724300249c771ebf9619ac</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>anthony.dotson@five9.com</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2017-11-30 23:20:52</sys_updated_on><when>onAfter</when></sys_transform_script></record_update>

    //We want to keep the browser from caching these responses
	response.setHeader("Cache-Control", "no-cache,no-store,must-revalidate,max-age=-1");
	response.setHeader("Pragma", "no-store,no-cache");
	response.setHeader("Expires","Thu, 01 Jan 1970 00:00:00");

	var entity = getParamAsString('entity');
	var isPhoneLog = getParamAsString('f9_phone_log');
	
	if ( !entity ) {
		response.setError(new sn_ws_err.BadRequestError("Missing or invalid entity value"));
		return;
	}
	
	if ( !request.body.data ) {
		response.setError(new sn_ws_err.BadRequestError("Missing or invalid body value"));
		return;
	}
	
	var responseArray = [];
	
	try {
		var body = request.body.data;
		var target = new GlideRecord(entity); 
		target.initialize();
		if ( isPhoneLog == 'true' ) {
			var duration = getPhoneLogDuration();
			if ( duration )
				body['duration'] = duration;
		}
		
		for (var key in body) {
		  if (body.hasOwnProperty(key)) {
			target[key] = body[key];
		  }
		}
		var retval = target.insert();
		return retval;
		
	} catch(e) {
		response.setError(new sn_ws_err.ServiceError(e));
	}
	
	function getPhoneLogDuration() {
		var duration = '';
		try {
			var startTime = body['start_time'];
			var endTime = body['end_time'];
			var gdt1 = new GlideDateTime(startTime);
			var gdt2 = new GlideDateTime(endTime);
			duration = GlideDateTime.subtract(gdt1, gdt2); 
			var dt = new GlideDateTime(duration);
			return duration.getValue().split(" ")[1];
		} catch(e) {
			gs.error(e);
		}
		return duration;
	}
	
	//make sure we always get strings from the parameter map
	function getParamAsString(paramName) {
		if (request.queryParams.hasOwnProperty(paramName))
			return request.queryParams[paramName] + '';
		return '';
	}

})(request, response);]]></operation_script><operation_uri>/api/x_f9_five9_adapter/five9_integration_api/v1/entity</operation_uri><produces>application/json,application/xml,text/xml</produces><produces_customized>false</produces_customized><relative_path>/v1/entity</relative_path><request_example/><requires_acl_authorization>true</requires_acl_authorization><requires_authentication>true</requires_authentication><short_description/><sys_class_name>sys_ws_operation</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>anthony.dotson@five9.com</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2017-05-30 20:53:15</sys_created_on><sys_customer_update>true</sys_customer_update><sys_id>0d909031db43f200249c771ebf961946</sys_id><sys_mod_count>28</sys_mod_count><sys_name>saveEntityRecord</sys_name><sys_package display_value="Five9 Plus Adapter" source="x_f9_five9_adapter">48cb0035db03f200249c771ebf961905</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_replace_on_upgrade>false</sys_replace_on_upgrade><sys_scope display_value="Five9 Plus Adapter">48cb0035db03f200249c771ebf961905</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_ws_operation_0d909031db43f200249c771ebf961946</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>anthony.dotson@five9.com</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2017-11-20 20:41:54</sys_updated_on><web_service_definition display_value="Five9 Integration API">619f08fddb03f200249c771ebf96191c</web_service_definition><web_service_version/></sys_ws_operation></record_update>

		}

		}
	} catch(e) {
		gs.error(e);

sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update sys_domain="global" table="sys_script"><sys_script action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><abort_action>false</abort_action><access>package_private</access><action_delete>false</action_delete><action_insert>true</action_insert><action_query>false</action_query><action_update>true</action_update><active>true</active><add_message>false</add_message><advanced>true</advanced><change_fields>false</change_fields><client_callable>false</client_callable><collection>x_f9_five9_adapter_five9_openframe_configuration</collection><condition/><description/><execute_function>false</execute_function><filter_condition/><is_rest>false</is_rest><message/><name>Five9 Update OpenFrame Configuration</name><order>100</order><priority>100</priority><rest_method/><rest_method_text/><rest_service/><rest_service_text/><rest_variables/><role_conditions/><script><![CDATA[(function executeRule(current, previous /*null when async*/) {

	gs.info("executeRule: " + current);
	var mainRec = new GlideRecord('x_f9_five9_adapter_five9_openframe_configuration');
	var config = {};
	mainRec.query();   
	if (mainRec.next()) {   
		config.bringapptofront = mainRec.getValue("bringapptofront");
		config.preselected_campaignname = mainRec.getValue("preselected_campaignname");
		config.recordinglinkurl = mainRec.getValue("recordinglinkurl");
		config.scriptedapiurl = mainRec.getValue("scriptedapiurl");	
		config.bringapptofront = mainRec.getValue("bringapptofront");
		config.phone_log_table = mainRec.getValue("phone_log");
		config.preselected_campaignname = mainRec.getValue("preselected_campaignname");
		config.recordinglinkurl = mainRec.getValue("recordinglinkurl");
		config.scriptedapiurl = mainRec.getValue("scriptedapiurl");
                config.client_id = mainRec.getValue("client_id");
                config.instance_url = mainRec.getValue("instance_url");
	}
	var entity = new GlideRecord('x_f9_five9_adapter_five9_entity_configuration');
	var entities = [];
	entity.query(); 
	while (entity.next()) {   
		var rec = {};
		rec.entity = entity.getValue("entity");
		rec.close_results = entity.getValue("close_results");
		rec.label = entity.getValue("label");
		rec.value = entity.getValue("value");
		rec.query = entity.getValue("query");
		rec.save_notes = entity.getValue("save_notes");
		rec.staging = entity.getValue("staging");
		rec.add_new_record = entity.getValue("add_new_record");
		rec.new_record_parameters = entity.getValue("new_record_parameters");
		entities.push(rec);
		var json2 =  new global.JSON().encode(rec);
	}
					
	var json =  new global.JSON().encode(entities);
	//gs.addInfoMessage(json);
	
	config.entityFieldMap = entities;
	var configJson =  new global.JSON().encode(config);
	//gs.addInfoMessage(configJson);
	
	// Now update the openframe configuration
	var openFrame = new GlideRecord('sn_openframe_configuration');
	var ofconfig = {};
        openFrame.addQuery("name", "Five9AdapterConfiguration");
	openFrame.query();   
	if (openFrame.next()) {  
		openFrame.setValue("configuration", configJson);
		openFrame.update();
	}

})(current, previous);]]></script><sys_class_name>sys_script</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>anthony.dotson@five9.com</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2017-09-12 16:02:22</sys_created_on><sys_customer_update>true</sys_customer_update><sys_domain>global</sys_domain><sys_domain_path>/</sys_domain_path><sys_id>d0cc77dbdb410700249c771ebf961934</sys_id><sys_mod_count>4</sys_mod_count><sys_name>Five9 Update OpenFrame Configuration</sys_name><sys_overrides/><sys_package display_value="Five9 Plus Adapter" source="x_f9_five9_adapter">48cb0035db03f200249c771ebf961905</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_replace_on_upgrade>false</sys_replace_on_upgrade><sys_scope display_value="Five9 Plus Adapter">48cb0035db03f200249c771ebf961905</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_script_d0cc77dbdb410700249c771ebf961934</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>anthony.dotson@five9.com</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2017-11-14 15:59:45</sys_updated_on><template/><when>after</when></sys_script><sys_translated_text action="delete_multiple" query="documentkey=d0cc77dbdb410700249c771ebf961934"/></record_update>

//until a Field Map is defined below - It's recommended to use the same field for coalescing
//as defined in SSO user_field or nameid attribute field
if(action == "insert") {
    //if no coalesce is set, then ignore insert
    if(!coalesceIsSet()) {
        ignore = true;
        gs.log("No coalesce is set, insert is ignored!");
    } 
}

//Returns true is coalesce field has been set for this
//transform map, false otherwise
function coalesceIsSet() {
    var fieldMap = new GlideRecord("sys_transform_entry");
    fieldMap.addQuery("map.name", "u_imp_saml_user_1mn6danlmm");
    fieldMap.addQuery("coalesce", true);
    fieldMap.query();
    return fieldMap.hasNext();
}
]]></script><source_table>u_imp_saml_user_1mn6danlmm</source_table><sys_class_name>sys_transform_map</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>anthony.dotson@five9.com</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2017-11-30 23:20:52</sys_created_on><sys_customer_update>true</sys_customer_update><sys_id>c3f65c49db724300249c771ebf9619a2</sys_id><sys_mod_count>0</sys_mod_count><sys_name>u_imp_saml_user_1mn6danlmm</sys_name><sys_package display_value="Five9 Adapter for ServiceNow" source="x_f9_five9_adapter">48cb0035db03f200249c771ebf961905</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_replace_on_upgrade>false</sys_replace_on_upgrade><sys_scope display_value="Five9 Adapter for ServiceNow">48cb0035db03f200249c771ebf961905</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_transform_map_c3f65c49db724300249c771ebf9619a2</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>anthony.dotson@five9.com</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2017-11-30 23:20:52</sys_updated_on><target_table>sys_user</target_table></sys_transform_map></record_update>

<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sys_ws_operation"><sys_ws_operation action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><active>true</active><consumes>application/json,application/xml,text/xml</consumes><consumes_customized>false</consumes_customized><default_operation_uri/><enforce_acl>6c701431db224300249c771ebf961916</enforce_acl><http_method>PUT</http_method><name>updateEntityRecord</name><operation_script><![CDATA[(function process(/*RESTAPIRequest*/ request, /*RESTAPIResponse*/ response) {

    //We want to keep the browser from caching these responses
	response.setHeader("Cache-Control", "no-cache,no-store,must-revalidate,max-age=-1");
	response.setHeader("Pragma", "no-store,no-cache");
	response.setHeader("Expires","Thu, 01 Jan 1970 00:00:00");
	
	var entity = getParamAsString('entity');
	
	if ( !entity ) {
		response.setError(new sn_ws_err.BadRequestError("Missing or invalid entity value"));
		return;
	}
	
	gs.info("updateEntityRecord.entity: " + entity);
	
	if ( !request.body.data ) {
		response.setError(new sn_ws_err.BadRequestError("Missing or invalid body value"));
		return;
	}
	
	gs.info("updateEntityRecord.body.data: " + request.body.data);
	
	if ( !request.body.data.sys_id ) {
		response.setError(new sn_ws_err.BadRequestError("Missing sys_id value"));
		return;
	}
	
	gs.info("updateEntityRecord.request.body.data.sys_id: " + request.body.data.sys_id);
	
	var responseArray = [];
	var user = gs.getUserID();
	
	try {
		var body = request.body.data;
		var target = new GlideRecord(entity); 
		//target.get(request.body.data.sys_id);
		target.initialize();
		//target.setNewGuidValue(request.body.data.sys_id);
		target.setValue("number", "CS0000005");
		target.setValue("active", false);
		for (var key in body) {
		//  if (body.hasOwnProperty(key)) {
			target[key] = body[key];
			gs.info("** ** **body[" + key + "] = " + body[key]);
		 // }
		}
		
		for (var key1 in target) {
		  //if (target.hasOwnProperty(key1)) {
		//	gs.info("target[" + key1 + "] = " + target[key1]);
		 // }
		}
		
		
		//var retval = target.updateWithReferences();
		//var retval = target.update();
		var retval = target.insert();
		return retval;
		
	} catch(e) {
		gs.error(e);
		response.setError(new sn_ws_err.ServiceError(e));
	}
	
	function getParamAsString(paramName) {
		if (request.queryParams.hasOwnProperty(paramName))
			return request.queryParams[paramName] + '';
		return '';
	}

})(request, response);]]></operation_script><operation_uri>/api/x_f9_five9_adapter/five9_integration_api/v1/entity</operation_uri><produces>application/json,application/xml,text/xml</produces><produces_customized>false</produces_customized><relative_path>/v1/entity</relative_path><request_example/><requires_acl_authorization>true</requires_acl_authorization><requires_authentication>true</requires_authentication><short_description/><sys_class_name>sys_ws_operation</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>anthony.dotson@five9.com</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2017-05-30 20:54:24</sys_created_on><sys_customer_update>true</sys_customer_update><sys_id>dcd09071db43f200249c771ebf96196b</sys_id><sys_mod_count>47</sys_mod_count><sys_name>updateEntityRecord</sys_name><sys_package display_value="Five9 Plus Adapter" source="x_f9_five9_adapter">48cb0035db03f200249c771ebf961905</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_replace_on_upgrade>false</sys_replace_on_upgrade><sys_scope display_value="Five9 Plus Adapter">48cb0035db03f200249c771ebf961905</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_ws_operation_dcd09071db43f200249c771ebf96196b</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>anthony.dotson@five9.com</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2017-11-20 20:42:13</sys_updated_on><web_service_definition display_value="Five9 Integration API">619f08fddb03f200249c771ebf96191c</web_service_definition><web_service_version/></sys_ws_operation></record_update>
